# Reddit API Credentials
REDDIT_CLIENT_ID="your_client_id_here"
REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET="your_client_secret_here"
REDDIT_USERNAME="your_bot_username"
REDDIT_PASSWORD="your_bot_password"
# To obtain these credentials:
# 1. Go to https://www.reddit.com/prefs/apps
# 2. Click "create another app..." at the bottom
# 3. Select "script" as the application type
# 4. Fill in name, description, and redirect uri (http://localhost:8080)
# 5. Click "create app"
# 6. The client ID is shown under your app name
# 7. The client secret is listed as "secret"
# 8. Use your Reddit account username and password for the bot
